{ Hello and welcome! This unique course has a clear purpose: to immerse you in many positions from different openings, helping you recognize and correctly implement healthy patterns. As you progress, you’ll become more familiar with typical opening ideas and plans, understanding when and why they succeed or fail. More importantly, your unconscious recognition of these patterns will improve, allowing you to choose strategically sound ideas rather than simply memorizing them. This course was created to deepen your understanding of opening moves rather than relying on rote learning. By exposing you to numerous examples – akin to the Woodpecker Method, but for opening strategy – you’ll develop pattern recognition through repetition. The material is designed to challenge your ability to constantly identify and apply these patterns. Whilst there are a few tactical elements, the real focus is on understanding which strategic concept takes priority in a given position. } 
1.--   *

