{ What happens if White pushes [d2]-[d4] in one shot? } 
1.d4 $1 { Now Black has two options: to leave the [e4]- and [d4]-pawns there, or to try to exploit the fact that White hasn't castled yet. } exd4  
2.cxd4  {[%csl Gd4]} {[%csl Ge4]} Bb4+  { This check is obviously possible because White hasn't castled yet. } 
