2.Bxh7+  {[%csl Rg8]} { The so-called 'Greek gift' is something Black has always to watch out for. } Kxh7  
3.Ng5+  {[%csl Rh7]} Kg6 $1 ( { The retreat ❌ } 3...Kg8? 4.Qh5 { leads to disaster. } ) 
4.Qg4  f5 $1 {[%csl Rg4]} { Attacking the queen. } 
