{ What is the quickest and most efficient way to clear the first rank and complete development? } 
1.Qe2 $1 { White brings their queen on a safe position and is one move closer to connecting the rooks. With the c- and d-files open, the rooks want to get there as soon as possible. } Rd8  { Not the only move, but a pretty logical one, developing the rook with tempo on the open file. } 
