2.Bb2  { What happens is White decides to capture on c5? See in the following variation. } Qc7 $1 {[%cal Gb8c6]} {[%cal Gb8d7]} {[%csl Rc4]} { This move develops the queen with tempo, as now White has to deal with [cxd4]. } 
3.Be2  {[%cal Gb8c6]} {[%cal Gb8d7]} { White will have to retreat this bishop sooner or later. Black can now choose where to develop his [b8]-knight. }  *

