{ After clearing the first rank for the rooks, the next step is to place them on the right files. The reason why this chapter focuses on the open and semi-open files is that they are the most natural playgrounds for the 'towers' to express themselves. However, the deeper concept is understanding that rooks work best on these types of files. The real skill lies in sensing which files will be the best for our rooks. Sometimes, it's straightforward when a file is already open; other times, it requires foresight to predict which files are likely to open or become semi-open. } 
