2.Bf4  {[%csl Gf4]} { White will successfully exchange Black's strong dark-squared bishop, as Black is unlikely to capture on [f4]. } ( 2. Bf4 { Doing so } 2...Bxf4 3.exf4 { would allow White to create • a strong [f4]-[f5] threat, • along with the possibility of the knight jumping to [e5], supported by both the [d4]- and [f4]-pawns. } )  *

