[FEN "5rk1/pq1bbp2/4pn1Q/2pp4/3P4/P1P1RN1P/3B1PP1/6K1 b - - 0 1"]

{ In this position, Black's main concern is their king’s weakness. As a general indication, when there is a queen next to our castle as in this case, White sacrificed a minor piece, we should focus on pushing the queen away as fast as possible. } Qb1+ $1 
