2.Re7  Rf7 $1 { Now Black can go on and eliminate White's rook once and for all. } ( { ✓ } 2...Rfe8 3.Ra7 Qc5 4.Rb7 ) ( { ✓ Funnily enough, the game ended after the repetition: } 2...Rce8 3.Rc7 Rc8 { . } ) 
3.Rxf7  Kxf7  
