[FEN "rn1qkbnr/pp2pppp/2p5/3p4/2P3b1/5NP1/PP1PPPBP/RNBQK2R b KQkq - 0 1"]
Nd7  { The most basic example of our topic. This move is a signal for us to consider the [d5]-capture. } 
2.cxd5 $5 cxd5  {[%cal Gd7b8]} {[%cal Gb8c6]} {[%csl Yd7]} { With the knight on [d7], Black will surprisingly need some extra time to regroup their pieces on better squares. } 
3.Nc3 $14 {[%csl Yd7]} { This type of position with the knight on [d7] is considered better for White. }  *

