3.Qc1  {[%cal Gc3a4]} {[%cal Gc2c3]} {[%cal Ga1a2]} {[%cal Rc7b5]} {[%cal Rb5d4]} {[%cal Rg7c3]} {[%cal Rb5c3]} { With the pawn still on [c2], White will eventually be able to play [Na4] and [c3], restricting Black's minor pieces. } Qb8  {[%cal Ga1a2]} {[%csl Rb2]}  *

