1.Bf1  {[%cal Gf1d3]} {[%cal Gb1h7]} { Here, as in the Carlsbad structure, the light bishop's dream diagonal is [b1]-[h7]. } ( { ✅ } 1.h4!? { is a clever move, taking space on the kingside. } ) ( { ✅ } 1.Nf1 { is a possibility, opening up the dark-squared bishop, but the priority should be given to the light-squared bishop. } )  *

