1.h4 $1 {[%cal Gg2h3]} {[%cal Rf6g4]} {[%cal Gh3d7]} {[%cal Re7e6]} {[%csl Rd7]} { Now it's time for White's [g2]-striker to get into position. From [h3], the bishop will keep under control many important squares, such as [g4], [e6], and [d7]. }  *

