3.Kh1 $1 {[%cal Gf2g1]} {[%cal Ge3e4]} {[%cal Gh2h3]} {[%cal Rf6g4]} {[%cal Rc6c5]} {[%cal Gd3b5]} { Giving some space for the bishop to retreat on [g1]. We will look deeper into this concept in the next chapters. }  *

