2.Bxd5  Qxd5  
3.Rxe7  Rg6  {[%cal Gc8h3]} {[%cal Gd5g2]} {[%cal Gg6g2]} {[%csl Ya1]} {[%csl Yb1]} {[%csl Yc1]} {[%csl Rg2]} { And Black has tremendous compensation for the sacrificed piece. }  *

