{ The Hedgehog structure is considered to be quite solid for Black, but especially with the bishop on [g2], White has an extra resource. How should White maximize their potential? } 
1.Nd5 $1 { A typical idea, exploiting the fact that the [c7]-queen is under the X-ray action of the [c1]-rook. } exd5  
2.cxd5 $1 Qb8  ( { ✓ } 2...Nc5 { would be followed by } 3.b4 { gaining back the piece and maintaining a stronger structure. } ) 
