{ By retreating the knight on [e7], [c8] is controlled, and Black's idea is to start exchanging heavy pieces along the c-file. How should White proceed? } 
2.Rc7 $1 {[%csl Gc7]} { Of course! White focuses on the 7th rank, avoiding the exchanges along the c-file on Black's terms. } ( { ❌ } 2.Rxc8+? { would blow up all the hard work White was doing along the c-file. } 2...Rxc8 { . Black solved the problems, with approximate equality. } )  *

