1.h4 $1 {[%cal Gh4h5]} {[%csl Re7]} { Once again, it's essential to keep tension and maintain the control of the c-file. [h2]-[h4] is a move that improves White's position, while Black is unable to counter White's dominance along the open file. } ( { ✅ } 1.g4 { takes away the [f5]-square from the knight and is actually good, as White's king is perfectly safe. } )  *

