{ In this kind of situation, strongholds are crucial, and one has to exploit them before their opponent manages to do it first. In this position, Black failed miserably from the positional point of view and White punishes the opponent with the typical move: } 
1.Rc6 $1 { If not now, Black would play ...[Rc5], and will be surviving! }  *

