2.Bb2  { White improves the position of their bishop, targeting [e5]. } ( { ❌ } 2.Nxe5 { is impossible because of } 2...Bf6 { , and Black wins material. } ) ( { The greedy ✕ } 2.cxb5?! axb5 3.Qxb5?? { would lose the queen after } 3...Ba6 4.Qc6 Rc8 { . } ) ( { ✓ } 2.Ne3 { would be met by } 2...Ne6 { . } ) Nbd7  
3.Bd3 $1 { Things are still complicated, but White has a tiny edge thanks to Black's weakened queenside. } ( { ✓ } 3.Ne3 { is still too soon. } 3...Ne6! { . } )  *

