2.Rab1 $1 ( { ✕ } 2.Rc2 { would be a mistake because of } 2...Nb6! { , and Black manages to block the files on the [c4]-square. } ) b6  
3.Rc2  Nc5 $1 { Black gives White a taste of his own medicine. } 
4.Bxb6  axb6  
5.Rbc1  Rc6 $1 
6.dxc5  Rfc8 $10 { Black successfully solved the issues of the c-file and the position is completely equal. }  *

