[FEN "r1b1r1k1/bpq2pp1/p1pp1nnp/4p3/3PP3/2P2NNP/PPB2PP1/R1BQR1K1 w - - 0 1"]

{ This is a position from the Giuoco Piano, where White has some space advantage and therefore an edge. How should White develop their initiative? } 
1.Be3 $1 { Besides protecting the center, White prepares the [Be3]-[Qd2] battery, which will hint on [h6]. } Be6  
2.Qd2 $1 {[%cal Ge3h6]} {[%cal Ga1d1]} {[%csl Rh6]} { Now, [Bxh6] sacrifices are a reality, and Black has to be really careful. Meanwhile, White has been reinforcing their center's stability. }  *

