{ A made-up position from a Queen's Gambit Accepted type of position. The c- and d-files are opened, and White is about to deliver the [Ba3] check. } Rd8 $1 {[%cal Rc1a3]} {[%csl Gd8]} { Black uses the tempo to activate the rook before it's too late. } ( { ✓ } 1...Ba6? {(similar would be 1...Bb7 would be careless:)} 2.Ba3+ Ke8 { would make it hard for Black to bring the [h8]-rook into play during the next phase of the game } ( 2...Kf6 is simply too adventurous. ) ) 
2.Ba3+  Ke8  {[%cal Gh8d8]} {[%csl Gd8]} { Having solved the [h8]-rook’s problems, Black will proceed with developing their queenside. }  *

