3.Bd3  Bb7  {[%cal Bc8a8]} {[%cal Ba8a5]} {[%cal Ba5c5]} {[%cal Gc5c8]} {[%cal Gc7c5]} {[%cal Bc7c8]} {[%csl Yc3]} { With ...[c7]-[c5] next, Black will develop harmoniously on the queenside, with the [a6]-[b5] powerful structure limiting White's [c3]-knight. }  *

