1.Kh2 $3 {[%cal Gb1h1]} {[%cal Gb3b4]} {[%cal Gb4b5]} {[%cal Gd4c6]} { White wants to take full control of the [c6]-square. Surprisingly enough, the best way to proceed for Black is to reroute their knight in order to keep the [c6]-square under control via [d7] to [b8]! }  *

