{ In several variations, the move [Bg5] pinning the [f6]-knight or ...[Bg4] pinning the [f3]-knight is a common idea. Now, 'asking the question' is a widely accepted practice with several benefits. If I had to decide whether to suggest playing ...[h6] or [h3], my answer would generally be 'yes.' However, there are exceptions. Let's explore this in more detail within specific openings. } 
